| [[Australian Capital Territory]] 
| Australian Capital Territory iri hagati ya Sydney na Melbourne. Ni ntebe y’ umurwa mukuru w’igihugu, Canberra. Canberra n’i w’inzego zikomeye z’igihugu nk’inzu y’inamanshingamateka (Parliament House), urwego rukuru rw’ubutungane y’Australiya (High Court).
|-
